name: 2016 Olio Quattrociocchi Olivastro
description: This extra virgin olive oil is produced exclusively from 100% Itrana variety olives locally grown on the Quattrociocchi Estate in Alatri. This oil has a fruity aroma enhanced by complex notes of grass, artichoke, green tomato and apple. Its flavor is pleasantly balanced in bitter and spiciness with hints of green almond.
